  <brief_title>Diabetes em Movimento® - Community-based Lifestyle Intervention Program for Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Diabetes em Movimento® - Community-based Lifestyle Intervention Program for Patients With Type 2 Diabetes: Effects on Health and Well-being</official_title>
